itunes:title: 42 A Servant of Strife
title: 42 A Servant of Strife
description:
Some protest war. Others, like Telamon, embrace it even as they hate it. "All things are born in strife, and all end in srife." But is that an answer? Telamon himself rejects it at the same time he espouses it. What lies beyond the Warrior Archetype? Can we get there? How?

New episodes every Monday
